com.cloudera.data.impl
Class Accessor

java.lang.Object
  com.cloudera.data.impl.Accessor

public abstract class Accessor
extends Object

Class to enforce "friend" access to internal methods in com.cloudera.data classes that are not a part of the public API.

This technique is described in detail in "Practical API Design" by Jaroslav Tulach.
